{
  "stem": "19055.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The, the Nazi movement was very, very strong all over the country, very well-supported.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And again, as a child, I remember when the head of the Nazi party nationwide-- his name was Szalasi, S-Z-A-L-A-S-I-- who became the president of the country eventually during the Nazis, he came to my town.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was not allowed to speak publicly, because Governor Horthy banned him because he, he was in competition with the government.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was in uniform.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He had a pockmarked face.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he stood in the middle of the marketplace on a podium.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were thousands of people around nit.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he hailed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And all he said, what kind of country do we want?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the crowd roared, Jew-free country, Jew-free country.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then he got off the podium.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he came around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was standing there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was shaking hands with everybody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I stepped back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Oh, god, I don't want to shake the hand of this man.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "What happened to me?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I'm here.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "What happened to him?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The Americans captured him in Austria after the war, Szalasi.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he was hung.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was mainly a, a farmland where we lived.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It's a plain farmers' country.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And the farmers were not too inclined to, to participate in any Nazi movement.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It, it was the-- it was the very poor-- the ones who eventually became communists after the war, the same people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] all in all, I, I don't have many bad words for my village.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Mostly decent people lived there, except for this few, who-- who came to the surface.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "During the early part of the war, what was life-- what life like for the-- well, for, for the Jewish population?",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
